   Yukich Clendon, Oscar M. M.; Burns, Bruce R., Univ Auckland, Sch Biol Sci, Auckland, New Zealand.
   Carpenter, Joanna K.; Monks, Adrian, Manaaki Whenua Landcare Res, Dunedin, New Zealand.
   Kelly, Dave, Univ Canterbury, Ctr Integrat Ecol, Sch Biol Sci, Christchurch, New Zealand.
   Timoti, Puke, Tuhoe Tuawhenua Trust, Rotorua, New Zealand.
