   Conran, John G., Univ Adelaide, Sprigg Geobiol Ctr, Sch Biol Sci, Benham Bldg DX 650 312, Adelaide, SA 5005, Australia.
   Bannister, Jennifer M., Univ Otago, Dept Bot, POB 56, Dunedin, New Zealand.},
